Zealand%2520Sign%2520Language.%0ahttps://www.quora.com/What-are-some-interesting-differences-between-American-Sign-Language-and-British-Sign-Language%0a%0a[[#contentends]]%0a----%0a(:GradedBy: TA_lili:)
