%2520the%2520Deaf%2520community.&text=As%2520with%2520ASL%252C%2520BSL%2520also,and%2520New%2520Zealand%2520Sign%2520Language.%0a%3c https://www.quora.com/What-are-some-interesting-differences-between-American-Sign-Language-and-British-Sign-Language%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
